8-10-06T15:59:50.000Z","msg":"我好掛住佢"},{"pid":"cbd2caf20419f291fce9c926dffaa00f2fb13831","tid":849553,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T16:06:35.000Z","msg":"你地分咗幾多年"},{"pid":"93692d4ec19605c06786d97bcc8bbe71df2327ee","tid":849553,"uid":193492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T16:20:13.000Z","msg":"中學暗戀咗個女仔三年<br />\n最後表白失敗咗（佢話未準備好）<br />\n佢喺香港讀大專 我去咗外國<br />\n一年幾喇<br />\n外國多咗唔同既人 照計應該識人識女係更加容易<br />\n但係我就偏偏仲係掛住佢<br />\n有次我個fd問<br />\n你係真係鐘意定執迷純粹想得到佢<br />\n嗰下我真係答唔到<br />\n畢業後已經冇乜來往<br />\n但係有時候都忍唔住whatsapp佢 跟住大家傾下自己既近況<br />\n以前相處既記憶好開心 但同時都令我而家好痛苦<br />\n老實講 如果有一日佢話佢準備好 我會好開心 long d都無所謂<br />\n但係事實唔係咁 唔肯忘記只係對雙方都唔好<br />\n所以有時候我都希望我地是但一個快啲搵到另一半 咁我就可以死咗條心<br />\n所以我明白你感受啊"},{"pid":"796248579857f724d473aa5f46ef8ceead96f668","tid":849553,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T17:30:57.000Z","msg":"一週的朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebefbbc1359e10eaa23b744308430363608e167b","tid":849553,"uid":210372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6bf05e1c389457750bf93640a654026b3a2c508","tid":849553,"uid":85146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:49:59.000Z","msg":"人若只如初見...."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"等閒變卻故人心"},{"pid":"f189e29464d91d7426d8c64120a15b82235b0ff1","tid":849553,"uid":30051,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T17:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> agger 大慨一世都真係冇人取代到"},{"pid":"5e91ea671266d590fadb0f4298da1e9aba6beb45","tid":849553,"uid":11989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f189e29464d91d7426d8c64120a15b82235b0ff1","tid":849553,"uid":30051,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T17:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> agger 大慨一世都真係冇人取代到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-